window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I haven't been a summoner for long, but I've already found myself three monsters and two Latents.</b></p> <p>The former are fearsome monsters that grant me power, while the latter are beautiful women who can cast their own spells.</p> <p>Together, we've become fugitives, with the world's First Summoner looking to take us down.</p> <p>To ensure the safety of not only Earth, I'm crossing into other realms to make pacts with the deadliest monsters I can find. Then, I'm going to use Fusion to combine them into even more powerful monsters. Once that's done, I'm taking the fight to Kyros.</p> <p>Easy, right?</p>"; 
